### **🔧 Technical Implementation**

#### **New API Endpoint**: `/api/ai/command` (POST)
```javascript
// Frontend calls this endpoint with JSON command
fetch('/api/ai/command', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify({ command: 'run system check' })
})
```

#### **Command Mapping System**:
```python
